# Tasks
# Calculate total sales
#.Find highest sales Find lowest sales.
# Calculate average sales.
# Count days with sales above average.Print all sales values above average.
# Count:Sales below 100  @@@
# Sales from 100 to 149
# " Find the second highest sales value.
